{"pageProps":{"news":{"_id":"5f0532323438f6b6ae3ad463","title":"国际学生保险必读","author":"","digest":"国际学生购买保险须知！实惠又有保障，学校要求保险都可以cover哒！","content":"<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 18px; background-color: rgb(255, 251, 0);\"><strong>在关注国际学生和访问学者保险的同学们请注意了（CSSA转发赞助商信息，任何商业行为与CSSA无关）</strong></span></p><p><br  /></p><p><br  /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 41, 65);\">ISO 留学生健康医疗保险-ISO Student Health Insurance</span></strong></p><hr  /><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;ISO留学生保险公司是美国留学生健康保险行业的领军企业，为留学生提供优质便捷的多语言客户服务。ISO提供符合Louisiana State University waiver要求的不同保险计划。25岁以下同学月费最低达到$31。同学们可以直接上网进行对比和购买, https://www.isoa.org/louisiana_state_university <span style=\"line-height: 1.6;\">在购买的时候请记得填写你们的LSU Student ID (89开头的号码) 。针对Fall学期，学校要求的保险日期是8/25/2016 到12/10/2016，大家不要买错。成功购买后，同学们会马上收到确认邮件。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"line-height: 1.6;\"><br  /></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 41, 65);\">关于Waiver form新公告</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 41, 65);\"></span></strong></p><hr  /><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.6;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">针对Fall semester，学校并不需要保险公司和同学们填写waiver form。我们公司会自动和学校直接report每个人的ISO保险coverage，这样可以简化waiver过程。请大家不用担心。<br  /></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;最后如需咨询保险问题，请拨打1（800）244-1180或者发邮件到 customercare@isoa.org 。</span></p><p><br  /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 251, 0);\">欢迎关注ISO微信平台（isoinsurance）和官方微博：@ISO学生健康医疗保险</span></strong></p><p><br  /></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(122, 79, 214); font-size: 12px;\">--------------------------------------------------</span></p><p><span style=\"line-height: 1.6; color: rgb(122, 79, 214); font-size: 12px;\">请关注主持我们的Facebook主页：www.facebook.com/LSUCSSA<br  /></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(122, 79, 214); font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(122, 79, 214); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">•</span><span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"color: rgb(122, 79, 214); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; white-space: pre;\">\t</span><span style=\"color: rgb(122, 79, 214); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">微信公众平台：CSSALSU</span><br  /></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(122, 79, 214); font-size: 12px;\">•<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"color: rgb(122, 79, 214); font-size: 14px; white-space: pre;\">\t</span>加入万能的CSSA Mailing List方法：发送姓名及申请至 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(122, 79, 214); font-size: 12px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; CSSA-L-REQUEST@LISTSERV.LSU.EDU</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(122, 79, 214); font-size: 12px;\">•<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"color: rgb(122, 79, 214); font-size: 14px; white-space: pre;\">\t</span>微博：路易斯安娜州立大学CSSA</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(122, 79, 214); font-size: 12px;\">•<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"color: rgb(122, 79, 214); font-size: 14px; white-space: pre;\">\t</span>网站：lsucssa.com（建设中）</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(122, 79, 214); font-size: 12px;\">•<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"color: rgb(122, 79, 214); font-size: 14px; white-space: pre;\">\t</span>投稿及建议意见请发送至：hr.cssa.lsu@gmail.com</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(122, 79, 214); font-size: 12px;\">•<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"color: rgb(122, 79, 214); font-size: 14px; white-space: pre;\">\t</span>人人网：已停止更新</span></p><p><span style=\"line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(122, 79, 214); font-size: 12px;\">--------------------------------------------------<br  /></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(122, 79, 214); font-size: 12px;\">路易斯安那州立大学中国学生学者联谊会</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(122, 79, 214); font-size: 12px;\">Chinese Students and Scholars Association (CSSA)</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(122, 79, 214); font-size: 12px;\">at Louisiana State University (LSU)</span></p><p><br  /></p><p><br  /></p>","url":"http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIwMjAwNDUxMg==&mid=502456577&idx=1&sn=d06c968b4f5dc1082eb8130165f089c9&chksm=0ee3004e399489588c00636f03359024d55c80798dbc0a39f36b963538fbe5cd88f9cae3a7d6#rd","thumb_media_id":"2EJIUVILHK642ZnYwwuOlhV6FFdLSQyDATpmFyuOVG0","thumb_url":"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/cGcYqtanUyuxfHiaApAAGHeB9FHHIIXV1c68ia2lU3EfCVbO8kR6HdPzKLRYD3PtYJpuloH2UJJhghWnY5X2bX7A/0?wx_fmt=png","update_time":"2016-08-31T02:37:38.000Z","media_id":"2EJIUVILHK642ZnYwwuOlobOfjJy8kTsF6JFeilIaaQ","createdAt":"2020-07-08T02:40:50.662Z","updatedAt":"2020-07-08T02:40:53.191Z","__v":0,"thumb_media":{"_id":"5f0532353438f6b6ae3ad464","name":"202067-46766-1kse093","alternativeText":null,"caption":null,"hash":"202067_46766_1kse093_1e23b40988","ext":".jpeg","mime":"image/jpeg","size":6.69,"width":400,"height":229,"url":"/uploads/202067_46766_1kse093_1e23b40988.jpeg","formats":{"thumbnail":{"hash":"thumbnail_202067_46766_1kse093_1e23b40988","ext":".jpeg","mime":"image/jpeg","width":245,"height":140,"size":3.81,"path":null,"url":"/uploads/thumbnail_202067_46766_1kse093_1e23b40988.jpeg"}},"provider":"local","related":["5f0532323438f6b6ae3ad463"],"createdAt":"2020-07-08T02:40:53.181Z","updatedAt":"2020-07-08T02:40:53.189Z","__v":0,"id":"5f0532353438f6b6ae3ad464"},"id":"5f0532323438f6b6ae3ad463"}},"__N_SSG":true}